{"tid":2275242,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國不再把東突厥列為恐怖組織","createTime":"2020-11-07T04:13:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T11:46:04.000Z","uid":29188,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4318ec01b5b8fa463cc9e08b41a1aa6ec014d7e2","tid":2275242,"uid":29188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T04:13:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.rfi.fr/media/display/8b9631d0-2024-11eb-bdbf-005056bff430/w:1280/p:16x9/Capture-73.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.rfi.fr%2Fmedia%2Fdisplay%2F8b9631d0-2024-11eb-bdbf-005056bff430%2Fw%3A1280%2Fp%3A16x9%2FCapture-73.webp&h=446c0ad5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em><span class=\"small\">美國國務院資料圖片 &copy; 路透社圖片</span></em><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\">自華盛頓方面消息，美國政府11月5日在聯邦公報（Federal Register）宣佈，不再把東突厥斯坦伊斯蘭運動列為「恐怖組織」。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n星期四公佈的聯邦公報內容顯示，美國國務卿蓬佩奧在通知中稱，根據《移民和國籍法》(INA) 212(a)(B)(II)修訂條款的授權，撤銷東突厥斯坦伊斯蘭運動（Eastern Turkistan Islamic Movement）的「恐怖組織」定列。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，美國等國是在2001年「911」恐怖襲擊發生之後將東突厥斯坦伊斯蘭運動列為恐怖組織的。該組織在2002年9月被聯合國安理會列為恐怖組織，也是中國公安部2003年12月第一批認定的四個「東突」恐怖組織之一。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB/20201106-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E6%8A%8A%E4%B8%9C%E4%BC%8A%E8%BF%90%E5%88%97%E4%B8%BA%E6%81%90%E6%80%96%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Fcn%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%2F20201106-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259B%25BD%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%258A%258A%25E4%25B8%259C%25E4%25BC%258A%25E8%25BF%2590%25E5%2588%2597%25E4%25B8%25BA%25E6%2581%2590%25E6%2580%2596%25E7%25BB%2584%25E7%25BB%2587&d=J7URIij%2BjV7QbFiEH5rjuAUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=05391581\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB/20201106-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E6%8A%8A%E4%B8%9C%E4%BC%8A%E8%BF%90%E5%88%97%E4%B8%BA%E6%81%90%E6%80%96%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87</a>"},{"pid":"fa63560d02a1c291cf50900ae8bcc6beecf2a91f","tid":2275242,"uid":176935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T04:15:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16ab3e40e23e8bf777ffc8bc400087cc610d90ac","tid":2275242,"uid":105924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T04:28:11.000Z","msg":"喜訊"},{"pid":"454207d9b63e4b4719a2c79b16ac29e624ea8fcb","tid":2275242,"uid":49329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T04:32:36.000Z","msg":"好事嚟。係共匪先 label 維族人係恐怖份子"},{"pid":"16e00fc753afe4e71d65200cc492364c60d46443","tid":2275242,"uid":29188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T11:46:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}